                            			<p>Account. The contractual arrangement wherein a TradeNAIRA Member has accepted our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy, and received approval to use the TradeNAIRA Services, including the purchase and sale of Currencies and to perform associated Transactions.</p>
										<p>Buyer(s). Member(s) that are submitting an offer to buy Currencies through the Service.</p>
